lop-identity, fairness, and experience-transcend specific conflicts and countries and are of importance to people everywhere.  aDescription based on information from publisher. 0aVictims of crimes (International law) 0aWitnessesxLegal status, laws, etc. 0aInternational criminal courts. 4aElectronic books.1 aKing, Kimi Lynn,eauthor.22aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)eissuing body.40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.10033319